These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, animation
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, bus
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | animation |
| Transport     | bus | roller  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, artichoke
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, tennis
1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | cranberry      | artichoke         |
| Sport   | water-polo | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, tomato
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | water   |
| Food       | tomato  | cabbage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, dutch
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, badminton
1. the dutch is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | canadian  | dutch |
| Sport         | surfing | badminton    |

